    <title>mac 搭建hexo 新手学习</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/01/31/mac-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAhexo/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/01/31/mac-搭建hexo/</id>
    <published>2018-01-31T02:18:54.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-01-31T07:11:41.450Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="安装自制软件homebrew"><a href="#安装自制软件homebrew" class="headerlink" title="安装自制软件homebrew"></a>安装自制软件homebrew</h3><p>  <code>ruby -e &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)&quot;</code></p><h3 id="安装nodejs"><a href="#安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="安装nodejs"></a>安装nodejs</h3><p> <code>brew install node</code> </p><h3 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h3><p>  <code>sudo npm install -g hexo</code>  </p><blockquote><p>密码为电脑admin密码</p></blockquote><h3 id="创建博客文件夹"><a href="#创建博客文件夹" class="headerlink" title="创建博客文件夹"></a>创建博客文件夹</h3><ul><li>1 <code>mkdir blog</code></li><li>2 <code>cd blog</code></li><li><p>3 <code>hexo init</code></p><blockquote><p>此时blog文件下会生成很多文件和文件夹，如下图</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://dalianmao97.github.io/public/images/first_one.png" alt="https://dalianmao97.github.io"></p></li></ul><h3 id="生成一套静态网页"><a href="#生成一套静态网页" class="headerlink" title="生成一套静态网页"></a>生成一套静态网页</h3><p>   <code>hexo generate</code>    </p><blockquote><p>在服务器上运行</p></blockquote><p>   <code>hexo server</code></p><h3 id="这时就可以在浏览器中输入http-localhost-4000查看网站首页"><a href="#这时就可以在浏览器中输入http-localhost-4000查看网站首页" class="headerlink" title="这时就可以在浏览器中输入http://localhost:4000查看网站首页"></a>这时就可以在浏览器中输入<a href="http://localhost:4000查看网站首页" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000查看网站首页</a></h3><h1 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h1><p>   与github账户关联<br>   首先你得有一个<a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a>账号,并新建一个名为[your_arrount].github.io的仓库。<br>   然后打开前面创建的blog目录下的_config.yml文件，再修改最下方的deploy为：</p><blockquote><p>冒号后面一定要给空格</p></blockquote>   <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">   type: git</span><br><span class="line">   repo: https://github.com/your_arrount/your_arrount.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">   branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装hexo的git部署"><a href="#安装hexo的git部署" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo的git部署"></a>安装hexo的git部署</h3><p>   <code>npm install hexo-deployer-git -S</code></p><p>   最后将生成静态页面部署到github的仓库中</p><p>   <code>hexo d -g</code></p><blockquote><p>当提示info deploy done:git 即上传成功，这时就可以通过<a href="https://your_account.github.io来" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://your_account.github.io来</a><br>   访问你的博客了</p></blockquote><h3 id="hexo的基本配置"><a href="#hexo的基本配置" class="headerlink" title="hexo的基本配置"></a>hexo的基本配置</h3><p>   以下上hexo配置文件_config.yml的基本内容和基本设置，更多个性化设置请参考<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a></p><p>`</p><h1 id="Hexo-Configuration"><a href="#Hexo-Configuration" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Configuration"></a>Hexo Configuration</h1><h2 id="Docs-https-hexo-io-docs-configuration-html"><a href="#Docs-https-hexo-io-docs-configuration-html" class="headerlink" title="Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/configuration.html"></a>Docs: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/configuration.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/configuration.html</a></h2><h2 id="Source-https-github-com-hexojs-hexo"><a href="#Source-https-github-com-hexojs-hexo" class="headerlink" title="Source: https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/"></a>Source: <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/</a></h2><h1 id="Site-页面信息"><a href="#Site-页面信息" class="headerlink" title="Site  ##页面信息"></a>Site  ##页面信息</h1><p>title: Who’s Blog  ##标题，即浏览器标签栏显示的内容<br>subtitle: Why so serious?  ##副标题<br>description:        ##描述，简介<br>author: Charles Wei  ##作者<br>language: zh-CN  ##语言<br>timezone: Asia/Shanghai  ##时区</p><h1 id="URL"><a href="#URL" class="headerlink" title="URL"></a>URL</h1><h2 id="If-your-site-is-put-in-a-subdirectory-set-url-as-‘http-yoursite-com-child‘-and-root-as-‘-child-‘"><a href="#If-your-site-is-put-in-a-subdirectory-set-url-as-‘http-yoursite-com-child‘-and-root-as-‘-child-‘" class="headerlink" title="If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as ‘http://yoursite.com/child‘ and root as ‘/child/‘"></a>If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as ‘<a href="http://yoursite.com/child">http://yoursite.com/child</a>‘ and root as ‘/child/‘</h2><p>url: <a href="http://wwww.charleswei.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://wwww.charleswei.me</a>  ##域名，后面自定义域名后，写在这里，用 .github.io的话，这里用默认的不用改<br>root: /<br>permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/<br>permalink_defaults:</p><h1 id="Directory-文件目录，可不改"><a href="#Directory-文件目录，可不改" class="headerlink" title="Directory  ##文件目录，可不改"></a>Directory  ##文件目录，可不改</h1><p>source_dir: source<br>public_dir: public<br>tag_dir: tags<br>archive_dir: archives<br>category_dir: categories<br>code_dir: downloads/code<br>i18n_dir: :lang<br>skip_render:</p><h1 id="Writing-静态页面生成属性，可不改"><a href="#Writing-静态页面生成属性，可不改" class="headerlink" title="Writing  ##静态页面生成属性，可不改"></a>Writing  ##静态页面生成属性，可不改</h1><p>new_post_name: :year-:month-:day-:title.md # File name of new posts<br>default_layout: post<br>titlecase: false # Transform title into titlecase<br>external_link: true # Open external links in new tab<br>filename_case: 0<br>render_drafts: false<br>post_asset_folder: false<br>relative_link: false<br>future: true<br>highlight:<br>  enable: true<br>  line_number: true<br>  auto_detect: false<br>  tab_replace:</p><h1 id="Category-amp-Tag-标签，可不改"><a href="#Category-amp-Tag-标签，可不改" class="headerlink" title="Category &amp; Tag ##标签，可不改"></a>Category &amp; Tag ##标签，可不改</h1><p>default_category: uncategorized<br>category_map:<br>tag_map:</p><h1 id="Date-Time-format-时间格式，可不改"><a href="#Date-Time-format-时间格式，可不改" class="headerlink" title="Date / Time format  ##时间格式，可不改"></a>Date / Time format  ##时间格式，可不改</h1><h2 id="Hexo-uses-Moment-js-to-parse-and-display-date"><a href="#Hexo-uses-Moment-js-to-parse-and-display-date" class="headerlink" title="Hexo uses Moment.js to parse and display date"></a>Hexo uses Moment.js to parse and display date</h2><h2 id="You-can-customize-the-date-format-as-defined-in"><a href="#You-can-customize-the-date-format-as-defined-in" class="headerlink" title="You can customize the date format as defined in"></a>You can customize the date format as defined in</h2><h2 id="http-momentjs-com-docs-displaying-format"><a href="#http-momentjs-com-docs-displaying-format" class="headerlink" title="http://momentjs.com/docs/#/displaying/format/"></a><a href="http://momentjs.com/docs/#/displaying/format/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://momentjs.com/docs/#/displaying/format/</a></h2><p>date_format: YYYY-MM-DD<br>time_format: HH:mm:ss</p><h1 id="Pagination-每页显示文章数，按需改"><a href="#Pagination-每页显示文章数，按需改" class="headerlink" title="Pagination ##每页显示文章数，按需改"></a>Pagination ##每页显示文章数，按需改</h1><h2 id="Set-per-page-to-0-to-disable-pagination"><a href="#Set-per-page-to-0-to-disable-pagination" class="headerlink" title="Set per_page to 0 to disable pagination"></a>Set per_page to 0 to disable pagination</h2><p>per_page: 10<br>pagination_dir: page</p><h1 id="Extensions-主题设置"><a href="#Extensions-主题设置" class="headerlink" title="Extensions ##主题设置"></a>Extensions ##主题设置</h1><h2 id="Plugins-https-hexo-io-plugins"><a href="#Plugins-https-hexo-io-plugins" class="headerlink" title="Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/"></a>Plugins: <a href="https://hexo.io/plugins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/plugins/</a></h2><h2 id="Themes-https-hexo-io-themes"><a href="#Themes-https-hexo-io-themes" class="headerlink" title="Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/"></a>Themes: <a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></h2><p>theme: indigo</p><h1 id="Deployment-git部署关联"><a href="#Deployment-git部署关联" class="headerlink" title="Deployment  ##git部署关联"></a>Deployment  ##git部署关联</h1><h2 id="Docs-https-hexo-io-docs-deployment-html"><a href="#Docs-https-hexo-io-docs-deployment-html" class="headerlink" title="Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html"></a>Docs: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</a></h2><p>deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repo: <a href="https://github.com/dalianmao97/dalianmao97.github.io.git" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/dalianmao97/dalianmao97.github.io.git</a><br>  branch: master<br>  `</p><p> ###最后生成部署</p><ul><li>1 hexo clean</li><li><p>2 hexo d -g </p><p>###然后就gogogo</p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
